# Both keys are optional — Furnace auto-generates them at startup if unset.
# Set them explicitly only if you need stable values across restarts.
#
# FURNACE_SESSION_HASH_KEY: keeps login sessions valid across restarts.
#   Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
#
# FURNACE_API_KEY: authenticates admin API calls (curl, CI scripts).
#   Copy from Admin UI → Config → Admin API Key after first start.

# FURNACE_SESSION_HASH_KEY=
# FURNACE_API_KEY=
